dc_description_s: This data represent school districts for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2019.[The tax parcel layer for Washburn County parcels is intended to represent parcels referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. Orthophoto evidence was used for conflicting or problematic descriptions. The polygons are created from the boundary linework.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For complete metadata visit: http://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
